            <li class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">&#8212;  <a href="eligibility" class="govuk-link">Eligibility</a></li>
            <li class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">&#8212;  <a href="how-to-claim" class="govuk-link">How to claim</a></li>
            <li class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">&#8212;  <a href="report-change-in-circumstances" class="govuk-link">Report a change in circumstances</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="govuk-grid-row">
        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
          <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l govuk-section-break--visible">

          <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you'll get</h2>
          
          <p class="govuk-body">Attendance Allowance is paid weekly at 2 different rates - the one you get depends on the level of help you need.</p>

          <p class="govuk-body">Attendance Allowance is not means-tested - what you earn or how much you have in savings will not affect what you get.</p>

          <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Attendance Allowance rates</h3>
          
          <table class="govuk-table">
            <thead class="govuk-table__head">
              <tr class="govuk-table__row">
                <th class="govuk-table__header govuk-!-width-one-quarter" scope="col">Rate</th>
                <th class="govuk-table__header" scope="col">Level of help you need</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
              <tr class="govuk-table__row ">
                <td class="govuk-table__cell">Lower rate - £68.10</td>
                <td class="govuk-table__cell">Frequent help or constant supervision during the day, or supervision at night</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="govuk-table__row ">
                <td class="govuk-table__cell">Higher rate - £101.75</td>
                <td class="govuk-table__cell">Help or supervision throughout both day and night, or a medical professional has said you might have 12 months or less to live</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <p class="govuk-body">If your circumstances change, you could get a different rate. You must <a href="report-change-in-circumstances" class="govuk-link">report a change of circumstances</a>.</p>

          <p class="govuk-body">You could get extra Pension Credit, Housing Benefit or Council Tax Reduction if you get Attendance Allowance - check with the helpline or office dealing with your benefit.</p>

          <div class="govuk-inset-text">
            If you get <a href="#" class="govuk-link">Constant Attendance Allowance</a> at the same time, your Attendance Allowance will be reduced by the amount of Constant Attendance Allowance you get.
          </div>

          <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">How you're paid</h3>

          <p class="govuk-body">All benefits are <a href="#" class="govuk-link">paid into your bank, building society or credit union account</a>.</p>
        
